Hey! My name is Charlie, and I’m with Movement Labs - we’ve started a new program called Beers and Ballots here in DC. It just kicked off last week; we go to bars and offer free beers to anyone who will text five friends and family members in swing states. (If you hit your metrics, volunteers also get a beer at the end of the night!) 

People have been really enthusiastic to talk to us so far; and we’re already partnering with way more bars than we can handle, so we could use volunteers! It’s one of the few ways you can contribute in person in deep blue DC. If you’re interested, here’s a mobilize link to get started: https://mobilize.us/s/cC4j8p

Also feel free to DM me if you have any questions. Hope to hear from you!
